ABOUT THIS REPOSITORY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Repository:     100 Days of Data Engineering
Author:         Ali Hegazy
GitHub:         https://github.com/ali-hegazy-ai
Year:           2026

This repository contains educational materials, code samples, notes, and
projects related to learning data engineering concepts over a 100-day period.

CONTENT TYPES COVERED BY THIS LICENSE:
- Markdown documentation and notes
- SQL query examples and exercises
- Python code and scripts
- Configuration files
- Project templates and examples
- Study guides and reference materials

